data.description: Discover country living in this meticulously maintained brick ranch that boasts a detached 28x40 Workshop w/ heat/AC for use as art studio, wood shop or gym. The formal living room has hardwood floors and a bay window. Entertain in the formal dining room or relax in the cozy family/den area with hardwood floors and a gas fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring wood cabinets, a pantry, and modern appliances, including a stainless steel gas stove and Bosch dishwasher. Three bedrooms offer comfort, while the primary  bedroom suite indulges with a private bath and dual vanity. Enjoy the outdoors on the front porch or the deck off the den. Side load 2-car garage, updated appliances throughout, this home is the epitome of leisurely living. Step into a world where elegance meets nature, and where your home is surrounded by the tranquility of blooming flowers, aromatic herbs, and the bountiful harvest of assorted fruit trees. Just a 5 minute drive to town for your shopping needs.
